CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper March 8, 1947, pg. 3, reads: "Delta Soror Honored - Mrs. Daisy Lampkin, who was recently made an honorary member of Delta Sigma Theta Sorority received high tribute last week when David Filner of the Centre Avenue Bakery delivered a huge cake at The Courier in honor of the noted NAACP leader and Courier vice president. Taking part in they social hour were Delta sorors who include: Virginia Stovall, Eva Mae Hannon, Gloria Johnson, Doris Handy, Mrs. Lampkin and Susie L. Smith. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Delta Sigma Theta sorority members Virginia Stovall, Eva Mae Hannon, Gloria Johnson, Doris Handy, honorary member Daisy Lampkin, and Susie L. Smith gathered around globe in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper office
